A branch can be cut from the swaying tree east of Rellekka. The branch may be turned into an unstrung lyre by using a knife on it, and the lyre may be strung by using golden wool on the unstrung lyre. Golden wool may be spun from golden fleece, an item obtained from Lalli. Doing so requires level 40 Crafting. The branch may be cut before starting The Fremennik Trials.

[[File:Branch detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''branch''' can be cut from the [[swaying tree]] east of [[Rellekka]]. The branch may be turned into an [[unstrung lyre]] by using a [[knife]] on it, and the [[lyre]] may be strung by using [[golden wool]] on the unstrung lyre. Golden wool may be [[Spinning wheel|spun]] from [[golden fleece]], an item obtained from [[Lalli]]. Doing so requires level 40 [[Crafting]]. The branch may be cut before starting [[The Fremennik Trials]].
